      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and tactile engagement. Crucial preventative maintenance has been performed, including rear subframe reinforcement and VANOS solenoid servicing, ensuring the structural integrity and variable valve timing remain within spec. The chassis maintains its signature balance with responsive damping and precise steering rack feedback. A mechanically sound example of the ultimate driving machine, ready for spirited canyon carving or daily enthusiast use.",
